sp.p:
By earth! by snares! by network! by cages! I never heard of anything more cleverly conceived;
                            and, if the other birds approve, I am going to build the city along with
                            you.

In the Ceramicus; for, to get a
       public funeral, we shall tell the Strategi that we fell at Orneae,
       fighting the country's foes.

Rosy Eros with the golden wings held the reins and guided the chariot;
                            'twas he, who presided over the
                            union of Zeus and the fortunate Hera. Oh! Hymen! oh! Hymenaeus!
